data.description:
Wonderful opportunity to own this lovely home with many upgrades! Nestled on a mature lot with a fully
fenced yard and detailed paver patio & firepit area. Welcoming front porch and a good sized entry with a
coat closet. Sharp Kitchen with upgraded custom cabinetry, tile backsplash and stainless steal
appliances. Attractive main floor living room area has pretty wood flooring and a wood burning fireplace. Dining area with a bayed window that opens to a large 3 season porch & deck with new boarding. Two good sized bedrooms on each level and a complete remodel in both bathrooms. Great lower level family room and 5th bedroom or office area. New Roof November 2023 & lots of extra storage including a built in garage closet, lower level under stair case storage and back yard storage shed! Move right in and enjoy!
